# VPS_superScript
#
Port 22
SyslogFacility AUTH
LogLevel INFO
LoginGraceTime 120
PermitRootLogin yes
StrictModes yes
PubkeyAuthentication yes
IgnoreRhosts yes
HostbasedAuthentication no
PermitEmptyPasswords no
PermitTunnel yes
KbdInteractiveAuthentication no
PasswordAuthentication yes
X11Forwarding yes
X11DisplayOffset 10
PrintMotd no
PrintLastLog yes
TCPKeepAlive yes
AcceptEnv LANG LC_*
Subsystem sftp /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server
UsePAM yes
Banner /etc/bannerssh
